<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

<h3>Login Accounts</h3>

<p>
    Login accounts are optional, you are not required to create an account if you want to use this website.
    Some parts of this website may require login account, for example submitting clan weights.
</p>

<p>
    Login account requires valid email address as username.
    We will send you an email confirmation message after you have registered your account.
    You can't use your account before you have confirmed your email.
</p>

<p>
    Your email address is used only for login purposes and self service password resets.
    If you have lost your password we can send a recovery link to your email address.
</p>

<p>
    You will receive an email when you create account, or when you try to recover your lost password.
    For all other email notifications you need to explicitly opt-in before we send you mail.
</p>

<p>
    We may delete or lock your account if we detect any misuse.
    We may delete inactive accounts or accounts that are not linked to any players.
</p>

<p>
    You can delete your account at any time.
    All traces of your deleted account and email address are removed from our systems after 60 days from account deletion.
</p>

<p>
    <b>We do not share your email address with third parties.</b>
</p>

<h3>Account Linking</h3>

<p>
    You can link all your Clash of Clans players to your login account.
    For the linking you need player tag (from My Profile page in CoC app) and API Token (from More Settings page in CoC app).
</p>

<p>
    If player is already linked to another login account, it will be moved to your current login account.
    If you delete your login account then all your player links are also deleted.
</p>

<p>
    <b>We may share your player tags with FWA Admins</b> if we need to troubleshoot problems or investigate issues related to your actions in this site.
</p>

<h3>Data Security</h3>

<p>
    IP addresses are visible in web server log files which are kept for 7 days.
</p>

<p>
    Login accounts and email addresses are saved in application database and may also be visible in application log files which are kept for 30 days.
</p>

<p>
    Backups of application databases and log files are kept for 30 days.
</p>

<p>
    Access to servers, databases and backup locations are restricted.
    All data is located in AWS datacenters in Europe.
</p>


